com.mousebird.maply

Class MapboxVectorTileSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.MapboxVectorTileSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QuadPagingLayer.PagingInterface

    public class MapboxVectorTileSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements QuadPagingLayer.PagingInterface
    The MapboxVectorTiles class is used to load Mapbox format vector tiles on demand over a certain area. You'll need to use this in combination with a QuadPagingLayer.

      • setCacheDir

        public void setCacheDir(java.io.File inCacheDir)
        Set the cache directory for fetched vector tiles. We'll look there first. There is no limiting or pruning going on, that directory will just get bigger and bigger.

        By default that directory is null.

        Parameters:
        inCacheDir - Cache directory for image tiles.
